                <div class="tit_nav">
                    <span class="tit_l">您所在位置：</span><a href="/Home/Index">首页</a><b>></b><span>案例信息</span>
                </div>
                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/2569" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MKT-0387</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9413 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">澳优乳业国际化经营战略与实施（之一）——初始国际化：轻资产运营</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Strategy and Implementation of Ausnutria’s Globalization (Part I)： Asset-light Operation for Initial</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">张景云，陈永涛等</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北京工商大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">澳优乳业</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">食品工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">13 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">国际化经营；澳优乳业；乳品品牌；营销渠道；品牌跨文化传播</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">International operation; Ausnutria; Dairy brand; Marketing channel; Brands’ cross-cultural communication</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">我国乳品企业的发展形成了一定规模，并涌现一些乳业巨头。然而，在国际化经营方面与国际乳品巨头相比，还有不少差距。经历多次食品安全事件后，消费者对本土乳品品牌信任度下降，使得我国乳品企业的品牌建设和开展国际化经营面临更大挑战。澳优乳业从2003年创业伊始即开展国际化经营，其战略基本上划分为轻资产运营、全球产业链构建和全球销售三个阶段。本案例介绍了其中第一个阶段——轻资产运营阶段（2003-2008年）的情况。主要涉及到品牌初创、渠道力取胜、“身份危机”、“换厂风波”等内容。通过该案例的学习，便于学生了解我国乳品企业开展国际化的原因，不同乳品企业开展国际化经营的不同方式，涉及到国际市场进入方式、品牌启动、渠道策略和利益相关者关系处理等知识点，有助于《国际市场营销》、《市场营销学》、《品牌管理》和《公共关系学》等课程或相关知识点的学习。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">With the development of Chinese dairy industories, some giant dairy enterprises sprang up. However, in terms of international operation, there is still a big gap between Chinese giant dairy enterprises and the oversea ones. After a number of  food safety incidents, consumers’ confidence in domestic dairy brands has declined，which leads to greater challenges for Chinese dairy enterprises both in branding and international business. Ausnutria began international business at its establishment in 2003，its strategy can be basically divided into three stages: Asset-light Operation, Constructing Global Industry Chain and Global Sales. This case introduces the first stage, asset-light operation(2003-2008). Including its start-up period, successful utilization of domestic channels,&quot;identity crisis&quot; and &quot;disturbances of plant changing&quot;,etc. Through studying this case, students can more easily understand the cause of Chinese dairy enterprises’ globalization and different ways to develop international business of different dairy enterprises, refering to several topics including international market entry mode, brand’s start, strategies of channel and relationships among stakeholders. All these above would be beneficial for students to learn the relative courses: International Marketing, Marketing, Brand Management and Public Relations.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2014</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《国际市场营销》、《市场营销学》、《品牌管理》、《公共关系学》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">国际市场进入方式、渠道策略、品牌启动、公众（利益相关者）</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2016-11</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">查看全文:</th>
